title: #256 Early Jizz
description:
It's a jet lagged, Irish Tuesday as Mark faces his angriest heckler ever at Hot Soup, and Joe sits on the tarmac for an eternity before he's accosted by a hooligan in Dublin! Check it out!

Subscribe to our Patreon for new bonus eps featuring Ron Bennington, Chris Distefano, Nikki Glaser, and Yannas Pappas. Plus, a new bonus vid with Joe, Robert Kelly & Ari Shaffir!
